Our paper tape is made of hypo allergenic and latex free material for a safe usage. It is comfortable, breathable and is made of high quality adhesive that is gentle on the skin and provides a long lasting bond .Ideal for repeated taping on fragile and sensitive skin especially in elderly patients.
Our artificial silk tape is superiorly strong, sticky, durable,multi purpose, non strechy medical adhesive tape. Suitable for dressing application for frequent dressing changes.
Non-woven tapes are tearable by hand. Their relatively low total thickness means they can conform to slightly irregular surfaces.
Our Polyethylene tape has a polyethylene backing with a rubber adhesive It can be used for variety of purposes such as sealing, color coding,moisture proofing etc.
